<!--
Starter manifest — copy this to <Inbox root>/categories.md and edit freely.
Delete what doesn't apply, rename anything, add categories of your own.
Full field reference: FORMAT.md
-->

## Finance
description: Banking, invoices, receipts, subscriptions, anything with a payment obligation.
destination: Finance/
policy: propose-actions
auto: true

## Tax
description: Tax authority letters, filings, annual statements needed for tax prep.
destination: Tax/
policy: file-only

## Health
description: Medical letters, lab results, insurance correspondence, appointment confirmations.
destination: Health/
policy: always-check-dates

## Family
description: School letters, permission slips, activities and correspondence for your kids.
destination: Family/
policy: always-check-dates

## Work
description: Employment paperwork, contracts, HR correspondence.
destination: Work/
policy: propose-actions

## Home
description: Lease, utilities, building management, household insurance and maintenance.
destination: Home/
policy: propose-actions

## Mobility
description: Vehicle, public transit, and travel bookings and receipts.
destination: Mobility/
policy: file-only

## Gwarancje / Warranties
description: Product warranties, proof-of-purchase for returns, appliance and electronics documentation.
destination: Warranties/
policy: always-check-dates
